    <item>
      <title>加拿大股市收复八月以来最大盘中跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/canadian-stocks-could-see-major-correction-after-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普上周末表示，将从周二开始对加拿大、墨西哥和中国征收关税，加拿大基准股指周一缩减跌幅，此前该指数一度创下自 8 月份以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/canadian-stocks-could-see-major-correction-after-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 14:05:52 GMT</pubDate>
